                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-2254-18370918 t18370918-2254-punishment-200"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">FLOOD</hi>—<hi rend="largeCaps">
                     <rs id="t18370918-2254-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18370918-2254-verdict-2" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
